Freezone.purpose: The cdfvalidator model is a json format file that can be used to check the content of a given CDF format file. See howto.txt file for more details.
Freezone.about-this-model: The current model example is based on the xlsx2skt_example.model.cdf CDF format file. It can be used to test the cdfvalidator module.
